name: Sleeping Bunny Blue, Purple or Yellow
description:
Our handmade Sleeping Bunnies are made from colourful cotton white tummies. 

Each Bunny has a child safe internal rattle to keep your little one entertained and has a strong loop which can be used with a toy saver strap to stop your bunny getting lost. 

Available in Yellow, Blue & Purple or as a limited edition Yellow with a Liberty print tummy.

Postage & packing additional £2.00

name: Organic Cotton Baby Blanket Ele Train
description:
Wrap your little one in two luxurious layers of certified organic cotton comfort.

This generously sized receiving blanket has a fantastic Ele Train print. The beautiful certified-organic cotton is backed with thick, unbleached US grown, organic cotton flannel. Perfectly gender-neutral and gorgeously soft. 

Made in Canada, and measuring approximately 27 x 34 inches, the blanket is double stitched for added durability. It is the perfect size for swaddling, cuddling, playing, burping, and traveling and Olive Homeware is the only UK supplier.

All fabrics have been pre-shrunk in chlorine/phosphate free laundry soap and tumbled dry. Machine wash in cold water/ tumble or hang to dry. Do not bleach.

Further images can be provided on request.

Postage & packing additional £4.00

name: Boat Nostalgia Tea Towel
description:
This tea towel features illustrations of fishing boats that are set in a small village on the North East coast of England. Navy and orange boat illustrations contrast with a light background making for a striking design that will induce thoughts of the seaside and British coast.

The tea towel would also look great in a frame. Why not put it on the wall of a nautical themed bathroom or in the living room of a coastal retreat.

We are proud to support British manufacturing and this product has been designed and printed in the North of England.

Made from 100% cotton, this product can be machine washed at 40 degrees and has a finished size of 46cm x 71cm.

The tea towel is folded and packaged with twine and printed label.

Postage & packing additional £2.70

name: Take the Bike Tea Towel
description:
This designs feature llustrations of bikes, drawn from photos taken when in the beautiful city of Paris. Scooters and bikes alike can be found at every turn in the city, being ridden beside the river, through one of the lovely parks or chained to intricate iron railings.

We are proud to support British manufacturing and this product has been designed and printed in the North of England.

Made from 100% cotton, this product can be machine washed at 40 degrees and has a finished size of 46cm x 71cm.

The tea towel is folded and packaged with twine and printed label.

Postage & packing additional £2.70

name: Coastal Tea Towel - Blue or Orange
description:
Jessica Hogarth's Coatal Tea Towels are inspired by the higgledy piggledy buildings that litter the north east coast of England.

Available in Navy Blue or Orange, dimensions 48cm by 78 cm.

Why not treat your home or a friend to one of these beautifully hand drawn cloths. 

Jessica's tea towels are hand screen printed and fixed onto 100% cotton.  They are suitable for machine wash, please do this before use.

This product is delivered packaged with twine and a home made label on brown recycled paper.

Postage & packing additional £2.70

name: A6 Note Books - Chevron
description:
An illustrative blank notebook in Chevron design by Jessica Hogarth.

This notebook is filled with 40 pages of blank A6 paper inside a highly illustrative matte cover. It provides a stylish way to store ideas, shopping lists or doodles!

Each notebook is packaged with a printed recycled brown paper band.

Notebooks purchased as a set are packaged back to back within one band.

All Jessica Hogarth stationery is designed and printed in the UK.

This is an A6 notebook measuring approximately 10.5 cm by 14.8 cm.

Postage & packing additional £0.75.

name: Illustrated Writing Set - The Tortoise & The Hare
description:
The tale of the race between a tortoise & a hare is beautifully illustrated in this Japanese writing set which includes 10 sheets of subtly textured paper with 3 coordinating envelopes.

Paper measures 13cm x 16cm

Postage & packing additional £1.70

(Pen not included, sorry)

name: Japanese Paper Tiger or Monkey Balloons
description:
These beautiful balloons are sent to us directly from Japan.  We have tigers and Monkeys in stock ready to be popped in the post.

Dimensions:  18cm diameter.

Each balloon is packed folded and all you have to do is blow into the hole at the top and the character expands into life.

To hang as a decoration or as part of a children's mobile simply attached twine to the center of a matchstick, without the tip and thread the matchstick into the hole to act as a bar inside the balloon.    

These balloons are not advised as toys for children under 3 years.

Postage & packing additional £0.75

name: Cork Bird House
description:
Look after the birds in your garden in style with this unique cork bird house designed by UK designer Gavin Coyle.  

This self-assembly bird house is designed to accommodate Blue tits, Marsh tits, and Coal tits.  

The die cut components are shaped into cones and linked together to form a natural nest shape. The material used is a cork/rubber composite which has great insulation properties, keeping the birds warm in the winter and cool in the summer.

The bird house is designed to be suspended from a rope and is shaped in a way to avoid inquisitive predators.

The assembled dimensions are 22cm x 16.5cm.

Postage & packing additional £3.70
